I am excited to collaborate with this Queensland Government organization in
the midst of a digital transformation. I am seeking a proficient Power
Platform Specialist to play a pivotal role in enhancing operational efficiency
and effectiveness. Your expertise will be instrumental in delivering cutting-
edge workflow automation, seamlessly streamlining interconnected processes
across the organization. By aligning with their Digital Strategy, you will
contribute significantly to achieving objectives.  
  
On a day-to-day basis, you will:  

  * Analyse workflow requirements and recommend / implement appropriate Power Platform solutions. 
  * Design end-to-end workflow automation solutions. 
  * Determine integration points with other systems and applications to create seamless processes. 
  * Automate repetitive tasks. 
  * Develop connectors and custom actions to extend Power Automate capabilities. 
  * Identify and resolve issues within Power Automate flows. 
  * Testing, debugging and optimisation of flows. 
  * Create comprehensive documentation for developed workflows, processes, and solutions. 
  * Ensure security measures are implemented to protect sensitive data within Power Automate flows. 
  * Set up monitoring mechanisms for performance tracking of Power Platform solutions. 
  * Use customisation and advanced features to extend functionality of applications. 
  * Ensure solutions align with best practices and industry standards. 
** Key knowledge and experience: **   

  * Demonstrated advanced knowledge and experience in workflow development and management using Power Automate. 
  * Excellent verbal and written communication skills. 
  * Understanding of security compliance in a digital environment. 
  * Excellent analytical skills. 
  * Ability to undertake multiple tasks with varying delivery schedules. 
  * Proficiency in the use of Power Platform applications, including Power Automate and Power Apps. 
This role is an initial 3 month contract with likely extensions. The role is
located with the Brisbane CBD close to transport.  
  
